node.text: Ranch is far and away the most popular salad dressing in the United States. But it's also so much more than that. It's a dipping sauce. A Halloween costume. Suit up and head to Harlem for the most soulful celebration of the summer, Thrillist Block Party. From a gospel open mic to a pop up roller rink to home-cooked barbecue and a ballroom competition, join us in supporting Harlem’s small businesses, community, and culture alongside the Queen of Hospitality and our Executive Producer, Tren’ness Woods-Black. Come on out Sunday, September 12 - link in bio for tickets! #THRILLISTBLOCKPARTY @doordash @queenofhospitality @sylviasrestaurant 

You must show proof of vaccination to attend the event.
